name: Brazilian BODY WAVE 14" Hair
description:
100% Virgin Brazilian Hair  AAAA Hair 4**** Hair 
BODY WAVE 
 14 inch 3.5- 4oz bundle
Brazilian Virgin Hair natural color ONLY 
that varies between 1b and 2 
Treat this hair with love and you can install multiple times. 
Wash and conditions like you would your own hair .
DO NOT USE OIL SHEEN USE ARGAN ,MOROCCAN OIL , OR ALCOHOL FREE SERUM USE HEAT PROTECTANT WITH IRONS
Apply Leave in conditioner or detangler before 
combing out after wash.
